exceptions.exn: In environment A : Set x : Map A Unable to unify "non_dist_chain ?M1851 (concat ?M1851 (single ?M1851 ?M1852) ?M1852)" with "forall (f : Map A -> Map A) (x0 : Map A) (n : nat), concat A (single A x) x = iteres A f x0 n -> non_dist_chain A (concat A (single A x) x) -> exists q : nat, S q <= n /\\ power (Map A) f x0 q = power (Map A) f x0 (S q)".
